text: Very Positive Environment  tho outside look small but inside is very spacious
Under renovation but still able to pray as there is a small area inside for less than 10 rows of jemaah
Undergoing renovations to accomodate more guests. Well preserved building, clean and convenient, just next to the road and shops.
Very nice and clean mosque. In this covid situation they're strictly follow save distance measure.

Alhamdullilah. Another majestic mosque nestled within the Teban Gardens estate. The audio system within the mosque is very strong too so that adds to the prayer environment as well. They have prayer areas for Level 1 & 2.

In view of COVID-19, only the back entrance is opened to public which serves well for those who drive as plenty of parking lots are available nearby.
